http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 6.947032108573254e-13, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}, {\"begin\": 990, \"end\": 995, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998441942474, \"rank\": 1.5580569660217816e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1024, \"end\": 1062, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Weightlifting_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Weightlifting Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Weightlifting_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Weightlifting_Federation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am so proud of you.\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1130, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know what you went through,\\\" Diaz told Yulo in Filipino during an interview with Olympic broadcaster Cignal.\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1241, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1234, \"end\": 1240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cignal_TV\", \"score\": 0.9999838786672004, \"rank\": 1.4211020505782858e-05, \"text\": \"Cignal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cignal_TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cignal_TV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am just here on the side.\", \"from\": 1243, \"to\": 1271, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am so proud that you overcame all the challenges.\\\"\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1324, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yulo recalled that back in Tokyo, Diaz showed him the precious Olympic gold, and it motivated him to win one himself.\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1443, \"entities